'''Bekee''' bu otu ana-kpo ndi English ma ndi ocha nile. Obu kwa he ana-kpo asüsü wo. Mgbe William Baike, onye English nwoke, biara na Igboland, ogwara ndi madu n'aha ya bula Baike. Maka otu ndi English di su asusu ha, mgbe ndi Igbo suoro ya, o dila nsogbu. Ha kpowa 'Baike' 'bekee', kpowazie ndi enyi ocha Baike, ndi bekee.
